rows.label: xs00090150_MSG0001
rows.name: Recognize the Habitat unit? That's where we're headed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00090150_MSG0002
rows.name: Watch yourself—that first step's a doozy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00090150_MSG0003
rows.name: We can jump if you like—you could handle the fall.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00090150_MSG0004
rows.name:
But the indigens down there are another story.
Some big, some mean—all nasty.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00090150_MSG0005
rows.name:
Given our options, the high road here
would be the safer way to go, relatively speaking.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs00090150_MSG0006
rows.name:
That said...whichever way you want to go,
I'll follow your lead. You decide.[ST:wait ]
